## This .gitattributes file automatically formats the EOL character in certain filetypes within the repository

# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
*          text=auto

## Source code
# JavaScript, TypeScript, c, and h source files
*.tsx                    text eol=lf
*.jsx                    text eol=lf
*.ts                    text eol=lf
*.js                    text eol=lf
*.scss                  text eol=lf
*.css                  text eol=lf

# Windows batch and PowerShell scripts
*.bat                   text eol=crlf
*.cmd                   text eol=crlf
*.ps1                   text eol=crlf

##### Other file types #####

## Text files and documentation
*.txt                   text
README*                 text
RELEASING*              text
CHANGELOG*              text
CONTRIBUTING*           text
INSTALL*                text
LICENSE*                text

## Non-text documentation
*.html                  text diff=html
*.pdf                   binary
*.json                  text eol=lf
*.rtf                   binary

## Git Properties
.gitignore              text
.gitmodules             text
.gitattributes          text